---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { withBase } from '@/lib/withBase';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Yanming Shao">
  <section class="about container">
    <div class="about__visual">
      <!-- Artwork by 6VCR (Eugenia Goncharova) — https://6vcr.com -->
      <img
        src={withBase('/art/hero-day.jpg')}
        alt=""
        class="about__visual-img about__visual-img--day"
        aria-hidden="true"
      />
      <img
        src={withBase('/art/hero-night.png')}
        alt=""
        class="about__visual-img about__visual-img--night"
        aria-hidden="true"
      />
      <div class="about__visual-grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="about__chip about__chip--left">
        <span data-lang-en>Research</span>
        <span data-lang-zh>研究</span>
        <span data-lang-ja>研究</span>
      </div>
      <div class="about__chip about__chip--center">
        <span data-lang-en>Art & Music</span>
        <span data-lang-zh>画与音乐</span>
        <span data-lang-ja>絵と音楽</span>
      </div>
      <div class="about__chip about__chip--right">
        <span data-lang-en><span class="about__chip-accent">Seeking</span> 26 Fall PhD</span>
        <span data-lang-zh><span class="about__chip-accent">Seeking</span> 26 Fall PhD</span>
        <span data-lang-ja><span class="about__chip-accent">Seeking</span> 26 Fall PhD</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <header class="about__header">
      <p class="about__eyebrow"><span data-lang-en>About</span><span data-lang-zh>关于</span><span data-lang-ja>概要</span></p>
      <h1>
        <span data-lang-en-block>Yanming Shao works on dexterous hands<br />and embodied AI.</span>
        <span data-lang-zh-block>邵彦铭研究灵巧手与具身智能。</span>
        <span data-lang-ja-block>邵彦銘は巧緻なロボットハンドと<br />具身AIを研究しています。</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="about__lead" data-lang-en-block>
        He is currently looking for Fall 2026 PhD opportunities. This site keeps a small record of papers, images, and music.
      </p>
      <p class="about__lead" data-lang-zh-block>
        他正在寻找 2026 Fall PhD 机会。这个站点也用来放论文、画面和音乐。
      </p>
      <p class="about__lead" data-lang-ja-block>
        現在、2026 Fall PhD の機会を探しています。このサイトは論文と絵と音楽の小さな記録でもあります。
      </p>
      <p class="about__collab" data-lang-en-block>
        His work centers on dexterous manipulation, data generation, and policy learning for embodied agents. In order of first collaboration, he has been glad to work with
        <a href="https://sist.shanghaitech.edu.cn/xcx/list.htm" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Chenxi Xiao</a>,
        <a href="https://yding25.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Yan Ding</a>,
        <a href="https://machengshen.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Macheng Shen</a>, and
        <a href="https://yaomarkmu.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Yao Mark Mu</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="about__collab" data-lang-zh-block>
        他的工作主要围绕灵巧操作、数据生成与具身智能中的策略学习，也很高兴先后与
        <a href="https://sist.shanghaitech.edu.cn/xcx/list.htm" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Chenxi Xiao</a>、
        <a href="https://yding25.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Yan Ding</a>、
        <a href="https://machengshen.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Macheng Shen</a>、
        <a href="https://yaomarkmu.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Yao Mark Mu</a>
        合作。
      </p>
      <p class="about__collab" data-lang-ja-block>
        研究の軸は、巧緻操作、データ生成、そして具身エージェントのための方策学習です。これまで、最初にご一緒した順に
        <a href="https://sist.shanghaitech.edu.cn/xcx/list.htm" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Chenxi Xiao</a>、
        <a href="https://yding25.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Yan Ding</a>、
        <a href="https://machengshen.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Macheng Shen</a>、
        <a href="https://yaomarkmu.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Yao Mark Mu</a>
        と研究をご一緒できたことを嬉しく思っています。
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="about__cards">
      <article class="about-card">
        <h2><span data-lang-en>Research</span><span data-lang-zh>研究</span><span data-lang-ja>研究</span></h2>
        <p data-lang-en-block>Bimanual grasp synthesis, finger coordination, and data generation for embodied manipulation.</p>
        <p data-lang-zh-block>关注双手抓取生成、手指协同，以及面向具身操作的数据生成。</p>
        <p data-lang-ja-block>双手把持生成、指の協調、そして具身操作のためのデータ生成に取り組んでいます。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="about-card">
        <h2><span data-lang-en>Seeking</span><span data-lang-zh>方向</span><span data-lang-ja>進学先</span></h2>
        <p data-lang-en-block>Looking for Fall 2026 PhD positions in embodied AI, dexterous manipulation, VLA, and agentic systems.</p>
        <p data-lang-zh-block>正在寻找 2026 Fall PhD，方向包括具身智能、灵巧操作、VLA 与 agentic systems。</p>
        <p data-lang-ja-block>Embodied AI、巧緻操作、VLA、agentic systems を軸にした 2026 Fall PhD を探しています。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="about-card">
        <h2><span data-lang-en>Elsewhere</span><span data-lang-zh>站外</span><span data-lang-ja>そのほか</span></h2>
        <p data-lang-en-block>Outside the lab: calligraphy, ruined landscapes, and long ambient tracks for late-night reading.</p>
        <p data-lang-zh-block>实验之外，喜欢书法、带废墟感的画面，以及适合深夜阅读的长环境音乐。</p>
        <p data-lang-ja-block>研究の外では、書、廃墟の気配をもつ絵、そして夜更けの読書に合う長い環境音が好きです。</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="about__links">
      <a href={withBase('/works')} class="about__link"><span data-lang-en>See Works</span><span data-lang-zh>看作品</span><span data-lang-ja>作品を見る</span> &rarr;</a>
      <a href={withBase('/travelogue')} class="about__link"><span data-lang-en>Read Travelogue</span><span data-lang-zh>看游记</span><span data-lang-ja>旅行記を読む</span> &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-top: clamp(3.2rem, 8vh, 6.2rem);
  }

  .about__visual {
    position: relative;
    min-height: clamp(210px, 36vw, 320px);
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    box-shadow:
      0 24px 44px -30px var(--c-shadow),
      0 1px 0 var(--surface-highlight) inset;
  }

  .about__visual::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(12, 22, 42, 0) 30%, rgba(12, 22, 42, 0.3) 100%);
  }

  .about__visual-img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 40%;
    transition: opacity var(--theme-switch-ms) var(--theme-switch-ease), transform var(--theme-switch-ms) var(--theme-switch-ease);
    animation: about-pan 24s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  .about__visual-img--night {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(1.04);
  }

  :root[data-theme='night'] .about__visual-img--day {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  :root[data-theme='night'] .about__visual-img--night {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1);
  }

  .about__visual-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 28px 28px;
    mix-blend-mode: soft-light;
  }

  .about__chip {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--surface-glass-a), var(--surface-glass-b));
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.64rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c-accent) 62%, var(--c-text) 38%);
    animation: chip-float 4.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .about__chip-accent {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, #d7ae74 72%, var(--c-accent) 28%);
  }

  .about__chip--left {
    left: 1rem;
    top: 1rem;
    animation-delay: 0ms;
  }

  .about__chip--center {
    left: 50%;
    top: 0.9rem;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    animation-delay: 500ms;
  }

  .about__chip--right {
    right: 1rem;
    top: 1.2rem;
    animation-delay: 1000ms;
  }

  .about__header {
    margin-top: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .about__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.11em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }

  .about__header h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    max-width: 18ch;
  }

  .about__lead {
    font-size: 1.03rem;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    max-width: 56ch;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .about__collab {
    margin-top: 0.9rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 64ch;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c-text) 78%, var(--c-text-muted) 22%);
  }

  .about__collab a {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c-accent) 52%, var(--c-text) 48%);
    text-decoration-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c-accent) 35%, transparent 65%);
    text-underline-offset: 0.18em;
  }

  .about__collab a:hover {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c-accent-2) 60%, var(--c-text) 40%);
  }

  .about__cards {
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }

  .about-card {
    padding: 1rem 1rem 0.95rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--surface-glass-a), var(--surface-glass-b));
    box-shadow:
      0 16px 30px -28px var(--c-shadow),
      0 1px 0 var(--surface-highlight) inset;
    transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-out-expo), border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .about-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c-accent) 52%, var(--c-border) 48%);
  }

  .about-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
  }

  .about-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
  }

  .about__links {
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .about__link {
    padding: 0.46rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--surface-glass-a), var(--surface-glass-b));
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.09em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c-accent) 65%, var(--c-text) 35%);
    transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .about__link:hover {
    transform: translateX(2px);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c-accent) 52%, var(--c-border) 48%);
  }

  @keyframes chip-float {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
  }

  .about__chip--center {
    animation-name: chip-float-center;
  }

  @keyframes chip-float-center {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-5px);
    }
  }

  @keyframes about-pan {
    0% {
      object-position: 50% 34%;
    }

    100% {
      object-position: 50% 66%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about__cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about__visual {
      min-height: 170px;
      border-radius: 15px;
    }

    .about__chip {
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    .about__chip--center {
      top: 0.72rem;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .about__visual-img,
    .about__chip {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
